<p>The Centre for Soldiers Wives &amp; Mothers<br/>92B Pitt St Sydney<br/>22.10.15</p>
<p>Dear Mr. Layton<br/>I am sending Mrs. Sullivan to you to see if you can give her some help.</p>
<p>She is the wife of a Reservist of the R. Irish &ndash; &amp; her allowance has been cut down 7/- per wk. &amp; is short of any money to go on with till paid again. on Nov 1st.</p>
<p>Yours sincerely<br/>E. H. Bennie &ndash;</p>
